{
  "texts": [
    "TTFS network: ΔW ðnÞ ij = À η dL dW ðnÞ ij, and compute the corresponding update δw ðnÞ ij in the space of the ReLU-network parameters.",
    "Then δw ðnÞ ij can be expressed as δw ðnÞ ij = MðW ðnÞ ij À η dL dW ðnÞ ij Þ À MðW ðnÞ ij Þ, where w ðnÞ ij = MðW ðnÞ ij Þ, see Eq.",
    "(2), see section \"Methods\".",
    "With the B1-model, MðW ðnÞ ij Þ is the identity function, hence δw ðnÞ ij = À η dL dW ðnÞ ij = ΔW ij.",
    "Therefore, for the B1-model the training trajectories of SNN and ReLU networks are equivalent."
  ]
}